1. The app is divided into 5 main sections 
    - app configuration
    - auth design
    - e-commerce design 
    - auth backend  
    - e-commerce backend 

2. Any Text Form Field placed in a Row it must wrapped with expanded 
3. If There any text in a row wrap it with expanded to prevent the overflow 
4. Wrap any check box with sizedBox and give it width and height = 20 to remove the default space around it
5. If you want to center some contents in a column wrap them with sized box and give its width width.infinity


1. there is two types of navigation bar : 1. navigation bar     2. navigation destination 
